<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Noël La Niege Special is the third game in the Noël series for the Playstation one console. This game is the sequel to Noël La Neige and features the same 3 female characters from that game: Yumi Tachibana, Ryo Midorikawa & Chisato Kadokura
                  <br><br>Again the game progress using different coversations (using the video phone or the computer) and selecting date for each girl and depending of the choices full motion video sequences will appear and other events.
                  <br><br>The game uses the same controls of Noël La Neige: each button is for a different thing like say yes, no or question.
                  <br><br>The gameplay is about choosing different answers or gather information to investigate in your computer network. Click on Interactive to start talking to Kaho or another girl right away. During the talk mode, there is a re-sizable data window in the middle of the screen. As your character talks with Yumi or any other character, topic icons stream across this bar, so click on them and they will be transferred to the data window.
                  <br><br>If you want to ask her about a particular topic, just click on the topic icon from your data window. In general, the more you ask the more clues you will get.
                  <br><br>The game features japanese voice acting and lots of full motion video sequences.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Noël La Neige the popular love adventure depicting the sequel to the software]. The three heroines who refused to college and graduated from high school, you can experience the last two weeks spent in Kamakura. [Previous] Noel La Neju can also enjoy a special conversation using the saved data can also enjoy mini-games such as neurasthenia and Hui facing away.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>First person perspective.</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Anime & Dating themes.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

